Package: protti
Title: Bottom-Up Proteomics and LiP-MS Quality Control and Data Analysis Tools
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Jan-Philipp",
           family = "Quast",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
